sql:
SELECT year, AVG(acceptance_rate) AS avg_acceptance_rate
FROM admission_rates
WHERE year = 2022;

SELECT AVG(retention_rate) AS avg_retention_rate
FROM graduation_rates
WHERE year = 2022;

external_knowledge:
- Top institutions are determined based on the lowest acceptance rates and highest graduation rates for the year 2022; 
- The ranking is specific to each region; 
- Total student numbers refer to both full-time and part-time undergraduate students combined; 
- The year 2022 is the specified academic year for which admission rates, graduation rates, and student numbers are considered.

